
  Hatenna    Psychic Type Pokémon

  Via the protrusion on its head, 
  it senses other creatures’ emotions. 
   If you don’t have a calm disposition, 
  it will never warm up to you. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Hatenna ► Hattrem ► Hatterene

